00f1bd322653678b.voiceContent: Large bookshelves and a fireplace... This would be a most comfy place to put my feet up.

20d0acefa659f375.voiceContent: But for once, I do want to take the trouble to make something nice.

250feee34e7647c8.voiceContent: ...I should let it be a surprise instead.

26425904ccbd0572.voiceContent: I think what makes this place so special is the fact that it was built personally by you.

266ffaf4f9260b3a.voiceContent: But you are special to me. I don't think about energy spent if it's for you.

419fe0c55469335f.voiceContent: Hmm... Is it just me, or have my interests become more domestic in nature since I met you...?

431fcd0cfbf3a517.voiceContent: I can offer you Sunsettia or Rose Bud Tea... And as for snacks, what kind of cake do you like?

43c659ec4c845d35.voiceContent: Not only are reference materials readily available, but you can initiate experiments at any time as well. This is truly a mage's ideal workshop.

4782172e7cefc649.voiceContent: You really know how to make me feel all warm and fuzzy inside.

54162f4ad895d614.voiceContent: You have good taste in literature.

552ee89e3e7264fe.voiceContent: *yawn* I'm so sleepy. I'm a little envious of the way you manage to stay so energetic even at this hour.

56ce3610ad097027.voiceContent: #You look so adorable with a little more red in your cheeks, {NICKNAME}.

57a824e07e4aee18.voiceContent: The number of people borrowing books is around the same as always. But lately, more people seem to be returning them on time than ever before.

5808370bc2f0ac55.voiceContent: If I were to start nitpicking, it would only ruin your creativity and the unique charm you bring to the place.

61af5c41329e4b3b.voiceContent: Seriously, though, I need to start getting prepared...

692150cf6e9ec636.voiceContent: Of course, I can't expect everyone to be as sensible as you, cutie.

7f4b2ceb7d09d203.voiceContent: Most of the time, I don't find these sort of things to be worth all the extra effort.

807518fd278bd03d.voiceContent: There is nothing I can't create if I put my mind to it.

87925f999f2ad93c.voiceContent: I'm sure you're keeping on top of everything that needs doing.

8c278e58ac51ca44.voiceContent: We can't have you underestimating me.

956a8cb61e15f665.voiceContent: And another that keeps the air fragrant and fresh. I'm quite fond of that one.

99b27d3584dd8f88.voiceContent: Don't you worry, I love it here.

9a4d4ee63c26f612.voiceContent: Ah, you're so easygoing. It's so relaxing spending time with you.

a7a9cb3ba2133bc2.voiceContent: I must reward you well for making this place so cozy.

ae410a94c2855287.voiceContent: Be sure to get enough sleep...

bbc2074f7d6bbae4.voiceContent: I was completely lost in thought.

c0a8fbe2e53489d2.voiceContent: Oh? A place suited for quiet research, I see.

c1d21ff48fb533a4.voiceContent: You really are a cutie after my own heart.

c23332c5f2b1479f.voiceContent: It seems that the citizens of the City of Freedom have become more conscious of time. Frankly, I'm quite relieved.

c28c5f26e9d585b0.voiceContent: I'd quite like to invite you to afternoon tea.

d2de88dc4686ca89.voiceContent: Hmm, perhaps instead of asking for your preferences...

d613fd14062182c4.voiceContent: I certainly wouldn't want that to happen.

d73de925b0a380e6.voiceContent: Aw, you're concerned for my well-being. Well, aren't you just the sweetest?

dc55ea4972ed4cf2.voiceContent: Oh my! Remind me not to add too much sugar, because you, cutie, are sweet enough already.

e764d2bd25d5f994.voiceContent: Oh! As a matter of fact, I concocted one that makes textiles softer to the touch.

ebf4feced33b8df6.voiceContent: They weren't requested by the Knights of Favonius, though. I just made them out of personal interest.

f6767990c0c74dcd.voiceContent: But if you find yourself struggling at any point, you know I'm always available to lend a hand.

fc9328087e76377c.voiceContent: If it weren't for my library work and potion-making duties, I'd love nothing more than to spend every day chatting with you like this.

0b3f15974e84ddf2.voiceContent: The electrical discharge caused by friction is only a little less shocking than love at first sight.

129771873d929be2.voiceContent: Paimon, are you able to float across?

68424a82db0306e9.voiceContent: The thought of putting my feet up and relaxing has me all fired up!

6d098f8f6c553205.voiceContent: I knew it. There is a strong elemental energy coming from deep within this temple.

6dfc63a116a7c57f.voiceContent: No wonder. Let me try to activate it with a bit of Electro power. Stand back, sweeties.

728965daad2d809c.voiceContent: When it comes to Wet enemies, I've got them covered.

9098878f0e35dc3b.voiceContent: Chain lightning can be set off between Electro-Charged opponents.

aeb3d5b92e421678.voiceContent: Let's ride this wind current, shall we?

bd36e38032eef42b.voiceContent: Good point. We'd better start looking for a way to get up there then.

e14a358fd2cbb351.voiceContent: I would love a slice of <color=#00E1FFFF>Invigorating Pizza</color> right about now...

e16d7fd1cec9f52d.voiceContent: Oh, another wind current. Let's ride it up from here.

f7fe1c7a0eb6c086.voiceContent: Break it and we can head home and relax.

05de3ac9a8a4ae37.voiceContent: Ah, dear little Collei. Every time she writes to me, she tries out new words and expressions she's learned recently... Hehe, no wonder she's improving so quickly. That wonderful and warmhearted master of hers must have helped a lot too.

0e72062324769a1b.voiceContent: Do you need me to lend a hand?

0edf2b681ee0d5c3.voiceContent: Come on Razor, that's it, good boy! Let's do some combat practice — I've found you the perfect partner. Hey! Come back!

0f414b2f6fa1e2be.voiceContent: Looks like I got carried away...

113915db108b752d.voiceContent: Let's spark things up a little.

1773bf6f0bce4d5c.voiceContent: Oh my... This is really... hmm...

1af1fd33833e15d2.voiceContent: Oh aren't you just the sweetest? Thanks, cutie, you just made my day.

2b4fdaba6625f578.voiceContent: Hehe, you've really got a knack for this, haven't you?

2b5ee7148de90bd6.voiceContent: *yawn* Good morning, Jean... Oh, it's you! Sorry, dear.

33fa15530b2a561b.voiceContent: What's that? You want to learn some Sumeru Akademiya magic? I'm afraid it might be a bit too much for you to handle right now... Hmm, though I suppose it can't hurt to teach you some of the basics. Here, start by reading the beginner's guide, it's only 800 pages or so.

3506bb594fdd062c.voiceContent: I've already tried to persuade you every way possible... *sigh* Have it your way, cutie. I can no longer go on pretending at this point — even a Hilichurl would see through the act. So be it, let me introduce you to the true Witch of Purple Rose.

3a54c34b5708b06e.voiceContent: Amber was just a young girl when she joined the knights, and in the blink of an eye, she's turned into such a strong young lady. I'm curious to see what she'll be like a few years from now.

4ea22fe8bb2568a7.voiceContent: When I practice my spells in weather like this, I can do half the work for double the impact. Haha, I'm just teasing.

56cf4e0443ec50dc.voiceContent: Fischl, yes, she's always in the library looking to borrow fantasy novels. She always returns her books three days early and looks after them very well. She's a good kid.

58f67d59a3b31071.voiceContent: I do rather envy Huffman for having such a caring little brother. Mika takes care of everything around the house and even looks after him when he's drunk... Ah, how nice it must be to lounge around all day without a care in the world... Hmm? What do you mean, I already do that? You're getting quite bold these days, aren't you, cutie?

5a3ccae765957344.voiceContent: *sigh* Perfect weather for sipping a cup of tea while gazing out the window.

5b0536a21b01fc4e.voiceContent: It's nearly time for afternoon tea.

5c2f2ab3c58407f0.voiceContent: Today's no good for going out... Hmm... Did I say that yesterday as well?

5c53780da36810f0.voiceContent: Feel free to use the alchemist's upstairs from the library whenever you want. But make sure you knock first... we wouldn't want you seeing anything you're not supposed to, now would we?

5d45529d93c9ca93.voiceContent: Jean is a gifted and dedicated leader. Seeing how hard she works makes even me want to help her out.

5f9c337c2f5fd346.voiceContent: So, which element would you like to learn about today?

648e6115ee972f88.voiceContent: You're in for a little shock.

64a5ec93aff76975.voiceContent: Every time I ask Noelle to dust off the bookshelves, I'm always left with the sense that the more exhausted I make her, the happier she becomes. Yes, who knows what's going on with her... *chuckles*

64cca9cbda08ccb3.voiceContent: Try not to enjoy this too much.

64ec6d25f0cff547.voiceContent: I knew I should have stayed home...

6696896045e302d7.voiceContent: *chuckles* If I were to recover my full power, who knows what kind of things might happen?

67c07571f06500f1.voiceContent: Surely you don't want me working overtime... That would be no good.

6964d6812ae05576.voiceContent: Last time little Klee wanted to use my workshop for her experiments, I had to say no, and she was angry at me for the rest of the day. *sigh* What happened the next day, you ask? She went off happily to play outside of course.

74e2d53bc554b1f2.voiceContent: Calla Lilies are a medicinal flower with antidotal properties. With them in hand, there's no need to worry about the side effects of any potions... Hehe.

77edd5b299b51a12.voiceContent: Albedo is quite the alchemist. Just say the word and he'll come up with a good solution. He's easy on the eyes too, just like you.

791ed03f0941e53b.voiceContent: Let me show you a thing or two, lest we let your efforts go to waste. *chuckles*

7a35478e7a7e1468.voiceContent: When I taught Razor how to utilize Elemental Energy, I never expected him to master the technique so quickly. Come to think of it, you're talented too. Maybe I could teach you a few tricks...

8951c4b3ca20b770.voiceContent: I've barely kept in touch with anyone from the Akademiya since leaving Sumeru, except for the occasional letters to my teachers out of basic courtesy. Fortunately, not every promising student turned out as lazy as I am... I heard that one of my juniors, Cyno, now leads quite the action-packed life.

8ef142f746d779bb.voiceContent: I'm not lazy, I just know to save my energy for when I need it most.

8ef6ad026213b73c.voiceContent: Hi darling, are you going to be Lisa's little helper? What? Me, a grand mage? That was a long time ago, I'm just a humble librarian now. *chuckles* Don't worry darling, I'll take very good care of you. So...

8f31f711953e1b77.voiceContent: I suffer from extreme pumpkinphobia. The fall harvest is a difficult time of year for me, as you can imagine. I wonder if it would be worth the trouble to make all the pumpkins in the world disappear...

9dbb486cbe540703.voiceContent: Here, take this amulet, it will bring you good luck. It's my birthday gift to you. I spent a long time making it, so don't lose it now!

a1c2fff1b3b5064e.voiceContent: You want to know about Diluc? Haha, in that case, I know someone else you should talk to.

a397025682f56444.voiceContent: I can be your teacher, your master, or your friend... or all three if you want...

a61b8c0e04345856.voiceContent: Such a calming breeze... Perfect for taking a nap, don't you think?

a7dd1e2b267808d2.voiceContent: Oh aren't you just the sweetest? Thanks, cutie, you just made my day.

b206a35b4e5c80d2.voiceContent: A Vision may seem like a great tool, but one day, the power one accumulates always finds a way to turn back on you. Should such a day come for me, so long as you're around... Ah, never mind.

b61bd066e56893d2.voiceContent: It must almost be time for a nap...

b7dcde379b84940a.voiceContent: As for Mona? She seems to be an excellent mage, but I'm not a part of their Hexenzirkel. The idea of Irminsul exploration and formal tea parties just leaves me cold.

bb50519eb75c031c.voiceContent: You're still up? I'm getting sleepy...

caecd4fb3ffefc5c.voiceContent: Oh my... This is really... hmm...

cda9bd7ad4218202.voiceContent: Hey darling, would you like to try one of my magic potions? There's no knowing what it will do to you until you try it, though... Don't say I didn't warn you!

cfe06184fbac18a9.voiceContent: My past? So, you want to get to know me a little better, huh? *chuckles* That's a story for another day. But I'm touched that you asked.

ddec84ab82242571.voiceContent: Why not keep me company for a while... There'll be plenty of time for work later.

de4abb7daa6a0c95.voiceContent: I like making my own vegetable soup. I put a big bunch of vegetables into a cauldron and stir it with a long spoon. What does it taste like? Here, why don't you try it for yourself. Open wide!

e07efd2e357538a2.voiceContent: I'll keep an eye on you.

e287f5e6a3cc1095.voiceContent: Try not to bother Sucrose if you're at a loose end, you'll only startle the poor girl. She's gifted at interacting with all sorts of exotic creatures — just hopeless when it comes to humans.

e4d927688942d7ce.voiceContent: Chances to practice should be left to you newcomers, no?

e5ea3ed8377f80a3.voiceContent: Visions? Ah, they're a necessary device in controlling the elements — with you being the sole exception, of course. Hmm... As for why that is, perhaps... we can find the time to experiment a little?

e9aab6e0f9650a78.voiceContent: Hehe, you've really got a knack for this, haven't you?

ecca0d2402c10cee.voiceContent: Have you heard Barbara sing before? Her angelic voice contains a magical healing energy. A different kind of magical energy from the one in my potions, of course. I wonder which one you prefer?

ee44ce61ba2f1303.voiceContent: Oh no, I'm gonna ruin my gloves.

ef6eba7364b1113d.voiceContent: I have some for you too.

f3c55e474990e6f2.voiceContent: Wait, one last thing... A kiss on the forehead from master to follower. Now you're my star pupil.

f8ac58ca4db2a134.voiceContent: I can see how hard you've been working today. Let me think of a way to reward you...

fdad4827dc2a2897.voiceContent: The interrogation room upstairs has sat there unused for two years now... It would be a much more lively place if Hertha would agree to let me use it as my private workshop... *sigh* She's such a spoilsport.
